thread.title: CNN: Trump Trip to Milwaukee Called Off Over Concerns of Protests

author: Josh Feldman
title: CNN: Trump Trip to Milwaukee Called Off Over Concerns of Protests
text:
— The Situation Room (@CNNSitRoom) January 31, 2017 
CNN reports tonight that President Trump ‘s planned trip to a Harley-Davidson factory has been called off over concerns from the company over protests. 
CNN’s Jeremy Diamond , citing an administration official, said that Trump was going to go on Thursday but then the company said “it wasn’t comfortable hosting the president amid a flurry of protests” panned for the visit. 
You can watch the report above.
